  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the antiviral efficacy, safety, and tolerability of sofosbuvir plus
      ribavirin administered for 16 weeks and 24 weeks in participants with chronic genotype 1
      (GT1) or genotype 3 (GT3) hepatitis C virus (HCV) infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
